oks?id=srzDCqnZkfUC&amp;pg=PA224\"><i>Encyclopedia of Political Thought</i></a>. Taylor &amp; Francis. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-415-19396-2\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-415-19396-2\">978-0-415-19396-2</a>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARepresentative+democracy&amp;rft.atitle=Direct+democracy&amp;rft.au=Budge%2C+Ian&amp;rft.aulast=Budge%2C+Ian&amp;rft.btitle=Encyclopedia+of+Political+Thought&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DsrzDCqnZkfUC%26pg%3DPA224&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-415-19396-2&amp;rft.pub=Taylor+%26+Francis&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Zur Soziologie des Parteiwesens in der modernen Demokratie. Untersuchungen \u00fcber die oligarchischen Tendenzen des Gruppenlebens (1911, 1925; 1970). Translated as <i>Sociologia del partito politico nella democrazia moderna&#160;: studi sulle tendenze oligarchiche degli aggregati politici</i>, from the German original by Dr. Alfredo Polledro, revised and expanded (1912). Translated, from the Italian, by Eden and Cedar Paul as Political Parties: A Sociological Study of the Oligarchical Tendencies of Modern Democracy (Hearst's International Library Co., 1915; Free Press, 1949; Dover Publications, 1959); republished with an introduction by Seymour Martin Lipset (Crowell-Collier, 1962; Transaction Publishers, 1999, <a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0765804697\" class=\"internal mw-magiclink-isbn\">ISBN 0-7658-0469-7</a>); translated in French by S. Jank\u00e9l\u00e9vitch, Les partis politiques. Essai sur les tendances oligarchiques des d\u00e9mocraties, Brussels, Editions de l'Universit\u00e9 de Bruxelles, 2009 (<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9782800414430\" class=\"internal mw-magiclink-isbn\">ISBN 978-2-8004-1443-0</a>).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Gemeindefreiheit als Rettung Europas. Grundlinien einer ethischen Geschichtsauffassung. Verlag B\u00fccherfreunde, Basel 1947. In 1983 republished under: \"Gemeindefreiheit - kommunale Selbstverwaltung\" (Adolf Gasser/Franz-Ludwig Knemeyer), in de reeks \"Studien zur Soziologie\", Nymphenburger, M\u00fcnchen, 1983.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"citation web\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Athenian_democracy#Selection_by_lot_.28allotment.29\">\"Selection by lot in the Athenian Democracy\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">1 October</span> 2013</span>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARepresentative+democracy&amp;rft.btitle=Selection+by+lot+in+the+Athenian+Democracy&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAthenian_democracy%23Selection_by_lot_.28allotment.29&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<span class=\"citation book\">\"1,5\". <i>Origins of Democracy in Ancient Greece</i>. Josiah Ober , Robert Wallace , Paul Cartledge , Cynthia Farrar (1st ed.). October 15, 2008. pp.&#160;17,105. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0520258099\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0520258099\">978-0520258099</a>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARepresentative+democracy&amp;rft.atitle=1%2C5&amp;rft.btitle=Origins+of+Democracy+in+Ancient+Greece&amp;rft.date=October+15%2C+2008&amp;rft.edition=1st&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.isbn=978-0520258099&amp;rft.pages=17%2C105&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Representative_democracy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"mbox-small plainlinks sistersitebox\" style=\"border:1px solid #aaa;background-color:#f9f9f9\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mbox-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Wiktionary-logo-en.svg/37px-Wiktionary-logo-en.svg.png\" width=\"37\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Wiktionary-logo-en.svg/55px-Wiktionary-logo-en.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/Wiktionary-logo-en.svg/73px-Wiktionary-logo-en.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1000\" data-file-height=\"1089\" /></td>\n<td class=\"mbox-text plainlist\">Look up <i><b><a href=\"//en.wiktionary.org/wiki/representative_democracy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wiktionary:representative democracy\">representative democracy</a></b></i> in Wiktionary, the free dictionary.</td></tr></table>\n<table class=\"mbox-small plainlinks sistersitebox\" style=\"border:1px solid #aaa;background-color:#f9f9f9\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mbox-image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Wikiquote-logo.svg/34px-Wikiquote-log